{"tid":1243051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求片求整理] 中信之後，夏慤道海富中心被圍攻險人踩人","createTime":"2019-06-19T09:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T12:03:15.000Z","uid":3560,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95133f279fbaf39ea0628f50b1e60031faae36b4","tid":1243051,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:51:24.000Z","msg":"其實喺中信出面，狗三面瘋狂放煙同速龍<br />\n迫晒本身企滿夏慤添美添華嘅人潮入海富樽頸<br />\n以下為我當日發夢第一身所見到、聽到後嚟再睇新聞嘅整合<br />\n因為我唔係聽到睇到晒所有嘢，所以可能會有錯漏<br />\n求片、相、整理返黑警意圖謀殺和平示威者嘅過程<br />\n<br />\n三點前，大家企滿添美、添華、中信、夏慤道。<br />\n人與人之間嘅距離大概係一個手踭位，夠開遮，但一定唔夠伸直手<br />\n我當時發夢係喺中信橋底傳物資<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQ1DSUo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQ1DSUo.jpg&h=b4165050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TxmAaHf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTxmAaHf.jpg&h=673e9313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三點三左右，中信事件發生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S4sccV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS4sccV1.jpg&h=2109aa76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z2g6qFRIbX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ2g6qFRIbX0&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=70f78703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z2g6qFRIbX0</a><br />\n<br />\n中信外面，狗冇停落嚟。入唔到中信嘅人就一路向中信橋底後退<br />\n而本身喺中信橋底就向夏慤道推<br />\n人與人嘅距離慢慢變成膊頭掂膊頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7o1gEEx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7o1gEEx.jpg&h=d766ac9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煙亦慢慢飄過嚟，我哋大部份人都有眼罩口罩，所以頂到<br />\n但人多又大煙，開始亂，圓筒形嘅物資（遮、鹽水、水）開始跌落地<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/tebiebaodao/612-06122019083956.html/61299996e2f5e026c11530556f47acb6cd54f1a53cd300a900372af67614f8b300b4fee8ba2-793a5a0173b0573a51b27a818b6665b953d15c0450ac6cea5f39/000_1hg1im.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Ftebiebaodao%2F612-06122019083956.html%2F61299996e2f5e026c11530556f47acb6cd54f1a53cd300a900372af67614f8b300b4fee8ba2-793a5a0173b0573a51b27a818b6665b953d15c0450ac6cea5f39%2F000_1hg1im.jpg&h=ca256e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張相係後期散咁少少人嗰時記者影嘅<br />\n可見到現場係極多石壆，地面唔小心跌咗極多物資，係<span style=\"color: red;\">非常極度容易仆街</span><br />\n但大家當時仍然好冷靜，好慢地向後退<br />\n<br />\n然後黑警喺中信方向、灣仔方向同中環方向<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不斷連續放咗十幾粒催淚彈</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2uVaKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2uVaKY.jpg&h=bcd0b537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環同灣仔天橋上嘅戰友向我哋夏慤道中間方向退<br />\n我哋已經極迫，好亂想執起地下嘅嘢<br />\n同時因為太多煙，眼罩口罩開始頂唔順，開始咳，開始痛，但完全冇機會沖乾淨<br />\n現場不斷嗌「向左！」「向右！」「向後！」<br />\n我哋開始要爬過石壆，所以開始移動得慢，但都叫做有秩序<br />\n片： <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rURjNc53K2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrURjNc53K2Q&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=9ea7ea71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rURjNc53K2Q</a><br />\n<br />\n沒有更仆街，只有更仆街<br />\n當大家眼罩矇晒，逼到不得了，眼耳口鼻極痛<br />\n速龍進場！！！遠處亦見到開槍嘅火光同聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5owkmVv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5owkmVv.jpg&h=3f01c746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中信方向（前面）有人大叫「跑！！跑！！」<br />\n海富方向（後面）嘅戰友就大嗌「女仔走先！！」然後抱啲女仔過石壆<br />\n大家向住海富中心跑，轉入樂禮街（窄極多）<br />\n而樂禮街本身已經有大量傷者坐喺地下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9L1QPP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9L1QPP.jpg&h=a7b4e25f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為實在太多催淚彈，煙亦都飄入海富二樓<br />\n而當入面有極多人取低眼罩沖眼，大量煙飄入嚟<br />\n有人哮喘，有人扶住一個勁辛苦嘅大肚婆經過我身邊（我後嚟唔知佢點）<br />\n然後又有人大叫「跑啊！！跑啊！！」<br />\n我估計應該又係門口有速龍<br />\n大家跑去PP方向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/1600/1*dDbp89v_KM2fB-Jq-zY3vQ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-images-1.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1600%2F1%2AdDbp89v_KM2fB-Jq-zY3vQ.jpeg&h=8b83e8e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當大家去到PP席地而坐去清潔返自己啲眼口鼻<br />\n又有人大叫「跑！！跑！！」<br />\n發生「自由閪」事件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cf83jKq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcf83jKq.jpg&h=5241ee23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HKVYB2LRACA&amp;t=7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHKVYB2LRACA%26t%3D7s&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=af0611ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HKVYB2LRACA&amp;t=7s</a><br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐之後我就收到短訊話原來開咗槍，有人吐血。<br />\n<br />\n我記得嘅夢就係咁<br />\n當時唔識驚，只可以盡力保護身邊嘅女仔<br />\n事後我真係覺得好恐怖，覺得自己差少少畀水樽／石壆／遮／口罩「戟」親跣親而搞到人踩人<br />\n當時太混亂，所以我無拍低記錄低<br />\n希望大家可以幫手整理返件事出嚟<br />\n<br />\n好恐怖，黑警根本係意圖謀殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"e816a5541aa19a1905612c98e56d8d2a4d9364ef","tid":1243051,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42a4b948689769ae380703186dbe409ec52c187b","tid":1243051,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:02:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"905278d52790e2fd0ad6484bc2f6d2eed5ff4c60","tid":1243051,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3c982d48ecb5bd3a6811df3373d70e3874b0ab","tid":1243051,"uid":56052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係基督徒、和理非，我都好攰&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242171</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ebdb0b2af572c049ff4ffd0419ee3242c83bc01","tid":1243051,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:12:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da30ca763800f78b0821e61bd9627aa082672ca7","tid":1243051,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93d09a049b862d5b43f6678a76e8f342f54d68a4","tid":1243051,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:03:15.000Z","msg":"推"}]}